---

<section class="manifesto section">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="eyebrow" data-reveal>Why we do this</p>
    <h2 class="manifesto__text" data-split>
      We think coffee got too fast. So we slowed it back down — one small drum,
      one careful batch, one honest cup at a time.
    </h2>
  </div>
</section>

<style lang="scss">
  .manifesto {
    background: var(--void);
  }

  .manifesto__text {
    margin-top: 2rem;
    max-width: 22ch;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5.2vw, 4.2rem);
    line-height: 1.05;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  /* Tint the closing phrase without breaking the word reveal. */
  .manifesto__text :global(.word:nth-last-child(-n + 6) .word__inner) {
    color: var(--amber);
  }
</style>
